<chapter xml:id="windows.shadow_dc.h">
<title><tt>__vic/windows/shadow_dc.h</tt></title>

<chapter xml:id="windows--ShadowDC">
<title><tt>windows::ShadowDC</tt></title>

<code-block lang="C++"><![CDATA[
class windows::ShadowDC : public windows::DC, private non_copyable
{
public:
    ShadowDC();
    ~ShadowDC();

    void Create(HWND hwnd);
    void Destroy();
    bool IsCreated() const;
};
]]></code-block>

<p>Virtual in-memory DC.</p>

<section><title>Class members</title>

<synopsis>
<prototype>ShadowDC()</prototype>
<postcondition><tt>!IsCreated()</tt></postcondition>
</synopsis>

<synopsis>
<prototype>~ShadowDC()</prototype>
<p>Calls <tt>Destroy()</tt> is <tt>IsCreated() == true</tt>.</p>
</synopsis>

<synopsis>
<prototype>void Create(HWND hwnd)</prototype>
<p>Creates shadow DC compatible with the specified window of the same size.
Throws on errors.</p>
<precondition><tt>!IsCreated()</tt></precondition>
<postcondition><tt>IsCreated() == true</tt></postcondition>
</synopsis>

<synopsis>
<prototype>void Destroy()</prototype>
<p>Destroys the DC.</p>
<precondition><tt>IsCreated() == true</tt></precondition>
<postcondition><tt>!IsCreated()</tt></postcondition>
</synopsis>

<synopsis>
<prototype>bool IsCreated() const</prototype>
<p>Returns <tt>true</tt> if the object has an associated shadow DC.</p>
</synopsis>

</section>

